data.name: lblInfo.Text
data.value: Instructions: - Mouse-over the top window to display controls for a single scan, auto-scanning, reset, show/hide this settings page, and for changing themes. - Clicking on any of the songs will show the song notes at the bottom of the application, in case you forget. - Left- or right-clicking on the Sacred Stones of Medallions with allow you to set reminders for yourself as to which dungeon they are in. - Left-clicking on a region will show you what checks are left in that area. Right-clicking shows already found checks. - You can double-click on a line in the output box to force it to be counted as checked. Hide those pesky freestanding items. - Use the settings below to enable tracking of specific things like Deku Scrubs and Cows. All settings save automatically. - Use the tricks settings to have logic better show what checks you can reach. - Right-click on anything on the settings page to display more info.
